Titolo: NCAA March Madness 2004

Anno: 2003

Descrizione: NCAA March Madness 2004 is the 2003 installment in the NCAA March Madness series.  Former Syracuse player Carmelo Anthony is featured on the cover. Commentary is done by Brad Nessler and "Mr. College Basketball" Dick Vitale as he is introduced in the game. This is the first entry in which players can pick their favorite schools. The menus are then stylized in the school's colors, and a cheerleader or mascot can appear on the main menu the school's fight song plays. The game plays similarly to NBA Live 2004.

Genere: Sports 

Valutazione: 81
